    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Facilities that are primarily engaged in the manufacture of paper or paper products, usually from wood, recycled paper, or other fiber pulp. Originally water-driven, modern paper mills are typically powered electrically.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
